self,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, property [&c.]; (T, * M, * Mgh, Msb, and L and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fwd","text_ar":"فود"},{"kind":"text","text":";) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AfAdhu","text_ar":"افادهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. therewith, (S, M, A, Mgh, O, L, Msb, K,) as used by some, (Msb,) having two contr. significations, (K,) though disallowed by others, (Msb,) or it is more chaste than the former; (Mgh;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tfy~dhu","text_ar":"تفيّدهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (M, and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fwd","text_ar":"فود"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He derived it, learned it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inferred it."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstfAd mnohu","text_ar":"استفاد منْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"derived, profit, advantage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"benefit, from him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAy^idapF","text_ar":"فَايِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"being understood.]"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Mgh","O","L","Msb","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}